                                <div class="map widget vothC112">
    <p>
        <b>
            <a href="#close" class="hide">
                [x] click to close
            </a>
        </b>
    </p>
    <div id="map_vothC112" style="width: 250px; height: 250px;"></div>
                        <p class="placename">
                Treblinka<br /><span class="alt">(Treblinka I, <br /><span class="alt">(Trenlinka II)</span>
            </p>
                                    <p class="municipality">
                <strong>Location:</strong>
                Treblinka, Poland<br />
                            </p>
                            <div>
                The largest of the &#34;Aktion Reinhard&#34; camps, this extermination camp was created to murder the Jews of the Warsaw ghetto and other ghettos in central Poland. From July 1942 to October 1943, more than 800,000 Jews and several thousand Roma were killed there.
            </div>
                            <style type="text/css">
.olLayerDiv{
width:250px !important;
height:250px !important;
}
</style>
<script type="text/javascript">
$(document).ready(function(){
    var map_id_vothC112 = new OpenLayers.Map('map_vothC112', {controls: []});
/*    gphy = new OpenLayers.Layer.Google(
                  "Google Physical",
                  {type: G_PHYSICAL_MAP,
                  'sphericalMercator': true,
     'maxExtent': new OpenLayers.Bounds(-20037508.34,-20037508.34,20037508.34,20037508.34)
}
               );
